<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.174588>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 3. Habitus. 1 — Hydroporus neclae sp. n. (holotype); 2 — H. longicornis (male; Germany, Bavaria); 3 — H. melanarius (male; Czech Republic, Bohemia)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/174588/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.174589>
    dc:description "FIGURES 4 – 13. 4 – 6 — Median lobe of aedeagus in ventral and lateral view. 4 — Hydroporus neclae sp. n.; 5 — H. longicornis (Germany, Bavaria); 6 — H. melanarius (Czech Republic, Bohemia). 7 – 9 — Left paramere. 7 — H. neclae sp. n.; 8 — H. longicornis; 9 — H. melanarius. 10 – 11 — H. neclae sp. n. 10 — gonocoxae; 11 — gonocoxosternum. 12 – 13 — Metacoxal processes. 12 — H. neclae sp. n. (holotype) 13 — H. longicornis (male; Germany, Bavaria)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/174589/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

